EASTERN CARIBBEAN SEA.
DOMINICA TO GUADELOUPE.
DNC 14.
15 FOOT F/V EXODUS, BLUE HULL, TWO PERSONS ON BOARD,
OVERDUE DOMINICA ISLAND (15-36.09N 061-21.98W) TO
FISHING GROUNDS IN VICINITY MARIE-GALANTE ISLAND
(15-52.16N 061-15.08W). VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
